<text><body>
<lb n="0032a17"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0032a18"/>
<lb n="0032a19"/>
<lb n="0032a20"/><head type="no">No. 1041</head>
<lb n="0032a21"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><note n="0032006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】寬弘三年寫東寺三密藏本</note><jhead>觀自在菩薩心真言一印念誦<note n="0032007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔法…出〕七字－【甲】</note><app n="0032007" word-count="7"><lem>法
<lb n="0032a22"/><note place="inline">千手千眼軌出</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0032a23"/>
<lb n="0032a24"/><byline type="Translator">大興善寺三藏<note n="0032008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔沙門〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032008"><lem>沙門</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>大廣智
<lb n="0032a25"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0032a26"/><div1 type="jing"><p>夫修行者欲念誦時。先<note n="0032009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔應〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032009"><lem>應</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>誦清淨真言七遍。
<lb n="0032a27"/>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0032a28"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd"><note n="0032010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甲本梵字無下同</note>&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A666;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>&CB02122;</zi><sg type="fangie">詩聿反</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-AF77;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0032011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">弟＝&CB14313;【甲】</note><app n="0032011"><lem>弟</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB14313;</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5AD;</t><t lang="chi">耨</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A663;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>戌</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-D9F9;</t><t lang="chi">馱</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5AA;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>曩</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F1;</t><t lang="chi">野</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合<note n="0032012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0032012"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0032a29"/>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1041.0032b" n="0032b"/>
<lb n="0032b01"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>賀</zi><sg><app type="＊" source="0032012"><lem>引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0032b02"/>
<lb n="0032b03"/><p>由誦此真言。<note n="0032013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">則獲＝七遍即【甲】</note><app n="0032013"><lem>則獲</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">七遍即</rdg></app>得三業清淨。則成以<note n="0032014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">功德法＝八功德【甲】</note><app n="0032014"><lem>功
<lb n="0032b04"/>德法</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">八功德</rdg></app>水灑浴身<note n="0032015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">心＝口意次【甲】</note><app n="0032015"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">口意次</rdg></app>。則結觀自在菩薩<note n="0032016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">印＝心密印以【甲】</note><app n="0032016"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">心密印以</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0032b05"/><p>二羽<note n="0032017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">相＝內【甲】</note><app n="0032017"><lem>相</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">內</rdg></app>叉<note n="0032018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔作〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032018"><lem>作</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>拳。<note n="0032019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔以〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032019"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>禪度出外<note n="0032020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔直〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032020"><lem>直</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00594;<note n="0032021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即成誦心＝誦【甲】</note><app n="0032021"><lem>即成。
<lb n="0032b06"/>誦心</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">誦</rdg></app>真言<note n="0032022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">七＝三【甲】</note><app n="0032022"><lem>七</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">三</rdg></app>遍。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0032b07"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC6;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>阿</zi><sg><note n="0032023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔去〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032023"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A4FA;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi><note n="0032024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚧＝嚕【甲】</note><app n="0032024"><lem>嚧</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">嚕</rdg></app></zi><sg><app type="＊" source="0032012"><lem>引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A64C;</t><t lang="chi">力</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E15D;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>迦</zi><sg><note n="0032025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔半音〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032025"><lem>半音</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>婆&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合<app type="＊" source="0032012"><lem>引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0032b08"/>
<lb n="0032b09"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>賀</zi><sg><app type="＊" source="0032012"><lem>引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0032b10"/>
<lb n="0032b11"/><p>由結<note n="0032026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此＝前【甲】</note><app n="0032026"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">前</rdg></app>印<note n="0032027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔及〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032027"><lem>及</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>誦真<note n="0032028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＋（故）【甲】</note><app n="0032028"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">言故</rdg></app>。即成三昧耶。又結前
<lb n="0032b12"/>印誦真言三遍。以印左<note n="0032029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">繞三匝則成＝旋三遍即【甲】</note><app n="0032029"><lem>繞三匝。則成</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">旋三遍即</rdg></app>辟除一
<lb n="0032b13"/>切諸魔障者。又結前印誦真言三遍。以印右
<lb n="0032b14"/>轉三匝<note n="0032030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">則＝即【甲】＊</note><app n="0032030"><lem>則</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">即</rdg></app>成結界。</p>
<lb n="0032b15"/><p><app type="＊" source="0032030"><lem>則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>想身前<note n="0032031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（有）＋八【甲】</note><app n="0032031"><lem>八</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">有八</rdg></app>葉蓮華。又結前印誦真言七
<lb n="0032b16"/>遍。以禪度向身招之。</p>
<lb n="0032b17"/><p>則觀自在菩薩。<note n="0032032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔并〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032032"><lem>并</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>蓮華部一切聖眾。皆來集
<lb n="0032b18"/><note n="0032033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">會＋（請加翳醯呬發遣改為&CB00753;瑳&CB00753;瑳）細註【甲】</note><app n="0032033"><lem>會</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">會<note place="inline">請加翳醯呬發遣改為&CB00753;瑳&CB00753;瑳</note></rdg></app>。則以二手捧閼伽香水器。當額奉獻誦真
<lb n="0032b19"/>言七遍。想浴聖眾。</p>
<lb n="0032b20"/><p>又結前印誦真言七遍。<note n="0032034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔則〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032034"><lem>則</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>成獻蓮華之座。</p>
<lb n="0032b21"/><p>又結前印誦真言三遍。<app type="＊" source="0032030"><lem>則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>成塗香供養。</p>
<lb n="0032b22"/><p>又結前印誦真言三遍。<app type="＊" source="0032030"><lem>則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>成<note n="0032035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（種種）＋華【甲】</note><app n="0032035"><lem>華</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">種種華</rdg></app>鬘供<note n="0032036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甲本養之次有又結前印誦真言三遍即成燒香供養十五字</note>養。</p>
<lb n="0032b23"/><p>又結前印誦真言三遍。<app type="＊" source="0032030"><lem>則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>成種種天<note n="0032037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔妙〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032037"><lem>妙</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>飲
<lb n="0032b24"/>食供養。</p>
<lb n="0032b25"/><p>又結前印誦真言三遍。<app type="＊" source="0032030"><lem>則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>成燈燭供養。</p>
<lb n="0032b26"/><p>又結前印<note n="0032038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔當心〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032038"><lem>當心</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>誦真言七遍。則想自身坐於
<lb n="0032b27"/>八葉蓮華臺中。相好威光具足圓滿等同觀
<lb n="0032b28"/>自在菩薩。於蓮華八葉。每一一葉上。各有
<lb n="0032b29"/>一如來入定。面向觀自在菩薩。行者<note n="0032039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以如是＝如【甲】</note><app n="0032039"><lem>以如是</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">如</rdg></app>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1041.0032c" n="0032c"/>
<lb n="0032c01"/>觀念極令分明。舉印於頂上<note n="0032040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">散＋（之）【甲】</note><app n="0032040"><lem>散</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">散之</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0032c02"/><p><app type="＊" source="0032030"><lem>則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>取念珠<note n="0032041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蟠＝盤【甲】</note><app n="0032041"><lem>蟠</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">盤</rdg></app>於掌中<note n="0032042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔合掌〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032042"><lem>合掌</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>當心。<note n="0032043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦＋（真言）【甲】</note><app n="0032043"><lem>誦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">誦真言</rdg></app>加持
<lb n="0032c03"/>念珠<note n="0032044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔真言〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032044"><lem>真言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>七遍。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0032c04"/><p type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A65D;</t><t lang="chi">尾</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A652;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>嚕</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A47C;</t><t lang="chi">左</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>曩</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E5;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>麼</zi><sg><note n="0032045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔鼻聲〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032045"><lem>鼻聲</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A64A;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0032046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00256;＋（二合引）細註【甲】</note><app n="0032046"><lem>&CB00256;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00256;<note place="inline">二合引</note></rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑<note n="0032047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＝婆【甲】</note><app n="0032047"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">婆</rdg></app></zi><sg>二合<app type="＊" source="0032012"><lem>引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0032c05"/>
<lb n="0032c06"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>賀</zi><sg>引</sg></yin></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0032c07"/>
<lb n="0032c08"/><p>則二手當心。各聚五指如未敷蓮華形。當心
<lb n="0032c09"/><note n="0032048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦＋（心）【甲】</note><app n="0032048"><lem>誦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">誦心</rdg></app>真言。不緩不急<note n="0032049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">歷＋（然）【甲】</note><app n="0032049"><lem>歷</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">歷然</rdg></app>分明不應出聲。寂靜
<lb n="0032c10"/>念誦每<note n="0032050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">與＝待【甲】</note><app n="0032050"><lem>與</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">待</rdg></app>真言後字聲<note n="0032051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（絕）＋齊【甲】</note><app n="0032051"><lem>齊</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">絕齊</rdg></app>移一珠。於<note n="0032052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔心〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032052"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>真
<lb n="0032c11"/>言句中去初後字。念誦之時勿令散亂。身心
<lb n="0032c12"/>凝寂更不異緣。唯觀本尊專注念誦。<note n="0032053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">則觀＝即【甲】</note><app n="0032053"><lem>則觀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">即</rdg></app>
<lb n="0032c13"/>想身前八葉蓮華上。有觀自在菩薩相好圓
<lb n="0032c14"/>滿處月輪中。復觀自身同彼觀自在菩薩等
<lb n="0032c15"/>無<note n="0032054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">差別＝有異【甲】</note><app n="0032054"><lem>差別</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">有異</rdg></app>。念誦數畢。捧珠頂戴起慈悲心發大
<lb n="0032c16"/>誓<note n="0032055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">願＋（願）【甲】</note><app n="0032055"><lem>願</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">願願</rdg></app>。一切有情所希<note n="0032056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">望＋（願世出）【甲】</note><app n="0032056"><lem>望</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">望願世出</rdg></app>。世間殊勝上願。速
<lb n="0032c17"/>得成就則安珠<note n="0032057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（於）＋本【甲】</note><app n="0032057"><lem>本</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">於本</rdg></app>處。</p>
<lb n="0032c18"/><p><note n="0032058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">又＝則【甲】</note><app n="0032058"><lem>又</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">則</rdg></app>結前印當心誦真言七遍。即成三昧<note n="0032059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耶＋（護身印）【甲】</note><app n="0032059"><lem>耶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">耶護身印</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0032c19"/><p>復以<note n="0032060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（其）＋印【甲】</note><app n="0032060"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">其印</rdg></app>加持自身五處。所謂額<note n="0032061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上右肩左＝左肩右【甲】</note><app n="0032061"><lem>上右肩左</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">左肩右</rdg></app>
<lb n="0032c20"/>肩心上及喉是名五處。<note n="0032062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">各＋（隨印處）【甲】</note><app n="0032062"><lem>各</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">各隨印處</rdg></app>誦真言一遍。加
<lb n="0032c21"/><note n="0032063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">持＋（已）【甲】</note><app n="0032063"><lem>持</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">持已</rdg></app>頂上散印。</p>
<lb n="0032c22"/><p>又結前印如<note n="0032064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">前＋（印奉）【甲】</note><app n="0032064"><lem>前</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">前印奉</rdg></app>獻五種供養。各誦真言一遍
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1041.0033a" n="0033a"/>
<lb n="0033a01"/><app type="＊" source="0032030"><lem>則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>成廣<note n="0033001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＋（殊勝）【甲】</note><app n="0033001"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">大殊勝</rdg></app>供養。則以二手捧閼伽<note n="0033002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（香）＋水【甲】</note><app n="0033002"><lem>水</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">香水</rdg></app>。當額
<lb n="0033a02"/>奉獻誦真言一遍。</p>
<lb n="0033a03"/><p>又結前印左轉一匝<app type="＊" source="0032030"><lem>則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>成解界。</p>
<lb n="0033a04"/><p>又結前印以禪度向外擲之誦真言三遍。舉
<lb n="0033a05"/>印安<note n="0033003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">頂＝於頂上【甲】</note><app n="0033003"><lem>頂</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">於頂上</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0032030"><lem>則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>成奉送一切聖眾。</p>
<lb n="0033a06"/><p>又結前<note n="0033004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">印＋（如前）【甲】</note><app n="0033004"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">印如前</rdg></app>加持。自身五處。<note n="0033005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔各誦真言一遍〕－【甲】</note><app n="0033005"><lem>各誦真言一遍</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0033a07"/>則成被甲。頂上散<note n="0033006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">印＝之【甲】</note><app n="0033006"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">之</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0033a08"/><p>修行者如是<note n="0033007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔依此〕－【甲】</note><app n="0033007"><lem>依此</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>祕密法要。精誠<note n="0033008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔念誦〕－【甲】</note><app n="0033008"><lem>念誦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>作
<lb n="0033a09"/>意修持。一切所為速得成就。世出世間諸願
<lb n="0033a10"/>圓滿。業障消<note n="0033009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">除＝滅【甲】</note><app n="0033009"><lem>除</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">滅</rdg></app>三昧現前。不轉此身騰空自
<lb n="0033a11"/>在隨意。即往十方淨土歷事諸佛。速成無上
<lb n="0033a12"/>菩提。</p></div1>
<lb n="0033a13"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><note n="0033010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（聖）＋觀【甲】</note><app n="0033010"><lem>觀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">聖觀</rdg></app>自在菩薩<note n="0033011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔心真言〕－【甲】</note><app n="0033011"><lem>心真言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>一印念誦法</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0033a14"/><note n="0033012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔八家…也〕四十三字－【甲】</note><app n="0033012" word-count="43"><lem><div1 type="W"><p>八家祕錄云。</p>
<lb n="0033a15"/><p>觀自在菩薩心真言一印念誦法<note place="inline">仁</note>不空</p>
<lb n="0033a16"/><p>此中仁者圓仁。即慈覺大師之諱也。此本
<lb n="0033a17"/>則慈覺請來也。</p></div1></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
</body></text></TEI.2>